{"tid":2406452,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"女同事磨紗玻璃會議室換衫事前提醒咪偷睇　港男出Po稱想向HR投訴","createTime":"2021-02-13T08:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T14:01:38.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93aacc650e8e5e5ad777787ebe67e755e25944af","tid":2406452,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210208/435420825202462720182935.jpeg/lKi2qQukv1Gr2FCWXB0PYGATA3MZlzjnklNwFZJTcBU?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210208%2F435420825202462720182935.jpeg%2FlKi2qQukv1Gr2FCWXB0PYGATA3MZlzjnklNwFZJTcBU%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=98490222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主在香港討論區上以「女同事喺Meeting Room換衫，係咪應該話畀HR知？」為題發文，指公司有女同事因為收工後趕要見朋友，所以直接在會議室更衣，「叫我哋唔好望」。不過由於會議室間隔使用磨紗透明玻璃，「根本會睇到啲肉色郁來郁去」，所以在想是否應該告訴HR相關事件。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都認為，女同事早已警告不要偷望，「人哋已經話咗你聽，叫你唔好望啦，做乜咁多事」。另外亦有人質疑，會議室可能有閉路電視，女同事的換衫過程已經被全程拍下。"},{"pid":"922e61d23ea4cffe808f8f28332eb4fe5a8b0dde","tid":2406452,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06ce75b9236f347199ec52d10ab9738d5e1c7d0","tid":2406452,"uid":72497,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"點解喺會議室換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb4745faa3579287c265de03c92bb3f3b911112","tid":2406452,"uid":38904,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"明知條女換衫都唔放枝cam入去<br />\n抵佢俾人屌"},{"pid":"4004f536ebacbba8fca9a149882aa4266ccb3bfd","tid":2406452,"uid":7854,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"又作故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f5a2d8a271f805f727ecf4951328a291c9abc5","tid":2406452,"uid":64576,"l